code:
sequenceDiagram
    actor Employee
    participant View as RenterView
    participant ViewModel as RenterViewModel
    participant RenterRepo as RenterRepository
    participant RackRepo as RackRepository
    participant Database

    Note over Employee,Database: The employee creates a rental agreement for a new customer.

    Employee->>View: enters details and clicks 'Rent Rack'
    activate View
    View->>ViewModel: command.Execute(renterData, rackID)
    activate ViewModel

    ViewModel->>RenterRepo: createNewRenter(renterData)
    activate RenterRepo
    RenterRepo->>Database: INSERT INTO Renters
    Database-->>RenterRepo: returnsRenterID
    deactivate RenterRepo
    
    ViewModel->>RackRepo: updateRackStatus(rackID, "Rented", renterID)
    activate RackRepo
    RackRepo->>Database: UPDATE Racks
    Database-->>RackRepo: confirmation
    deactivate RackRepo

    ViewModel-->>ViewModel: updateViewModelProperties()
    ViewModel-->>View: (data binding)
    deactivate ViewModel
    View-->>Employee: displays confirmation message
    deactivate View
